The '''Universal Conscription Bill''' was an act passed by [[New Republic Senate/Legends|New Republic Senate]] in [[25 ABY/Legends|25.5 ABY]] in response to the [[Battle of Ithor]]. It provided for widespread mandated drafting into the [[New Republic Defense Force/Legends|New Republic Defense Force]] during the [[Yuuzhan Vong]]'s [[Yuuzhan Vong War|invasion]] of [[The galaxy/Legends|the galaxy]].

